Package: kRypto
Type: Package
Title: Pull Cryptocurrency Data in Tidy Format Form Coinmarketcap API
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Adelmo", "Filho", email = "adelmo.aguiar.filho@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A wrapper for pulling cryptocurrency data in tidy format form coinmarketcap API <https://api.coinmarketcap.com>. By automatically batching API requests, it allows you to enter an cryptocurrency's name and retrieve their historical or today data.
URL: https://github.com/adelmofilho/kRypto
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0), dplyr
Imports: purrr, httr, rvest, stringr, xml2, lubridate, stringi
Suggests: testthat
